"{\"uid\": \"newstalk.com-news-hosting-2072-olympics-would-celebrate-150-years-of-irish-independence-senator-1754370\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Live  19:00-22:00  19.38 12 Aug 2024  Share this article  19.38 12 Aug 2024  Share this article  Hosting the Olympic Games in 2072 would be a fitting way to celebrate 150 of Ireland's participation as an independent nation, a Fianna F\\u00e1il Senator has said.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 255, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 174, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}, {\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 237, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fianna_F\\u00e1il\", \"score\": 0.9999999994315658, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Fianna F\\u00e1il\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fianna_F\\u00e1il\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Fianna_F\\u00e1il\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ireland has never hosted the Olympics and currently lacks the sporting and public transport infrastructure for a successful bid.\", \"from\": 257, \"to\": 385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 257, \"end\": 264, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, Senator Malcolm Byrne said Ireland needs to be \\\"ambitious\\\" as a country and should start laying the groundwork for a bid now.\", \"from\": 387, \"to\": 521, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 404, \"end\": 417, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Byrne\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Malcolm Byrne\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malcolm_Byrne\"}, {\"begin\": 423, \"end\": 430, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Why I like the idea of 2072 is that it marks 150 years since Ireland as an independent State first started taking part in the Olympics,\\\" he toldLunchtime Live.\", \"from\": 525, \"to\": 685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 587, \"end\": 594, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I appreciate it's five decades away but I think one of our challenges in this country is that we have not engaged a lot in long-term planning and I think we need to look at engaging in a lot more long-term planning.\", \"from\": 687, \"to\": 903, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We also need to talk about the type of infrastructure that we need to be able to support our elite athletes.\\\"\", \"from\": 905, \"to\": 1015, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The atmosphere is electric at the#Olympicteam homecoming ?pic.twitter.com/LqWbCAHG4C  - NewstalkFM (@NewstalkFM)August 12, 2024    Senator Byrne said he could understand why many people who think an Irish bid for the Olympics would seem unlikely to succeed at the moment.\", \"from\": 1017, \"to\": 1288, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1156, \"end\": 1161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\", \"score\": 0.8229190579868942, \"rank\": 0.215186341922043, \"text\": \"Byrne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\"}, {\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1221, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.947168903278524, \"rank\": 0.037697725891008116, \"text\": \"Irish\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, he added that Ireland will be a very different country by 2072.\", \"from\": 1290, \"to\": 1362, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1313, \"end\": 1320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If you could imagine in 1970s Ireland what 2020s Ireland would be, can you just imagine what 2070s Ireland might end up looking like?\\\"\", \"from\": 1364, \"to\": 1499, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1395, \"end\": 1402, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"he said.\", \"from\": 1500, \"to\": 1508, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Senator Byrne also said a joint bid with \\\"one of our nearest neighbours\\\" would be an idea worth considering -in the same way Britain and Ireland are jointly hosting Euro 2028.\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1685, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1518, \"end\": 1523, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\", \"score\": 0.8229190579868942, \"rank\": 0.215186341922043, \"text\": \"Byrne\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Francis_John_Byrne\"}, {\"begin\": 1635, \"end\": 1642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9999659196355788, \"rank\": 2.585206986096567e-05, \"text\": \"Britain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}, {\"begin\": 1647, \"end\": 1654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"score\": 0.9999879400422365, \"rank\": 1.1085127232586342e-05, \"text\": \"Ireland\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Republic_of_Ireland\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are a country that can punch above our weight, what is it that would require us to get to the kind of standard that our athletes\\u2026 [would have] world class facilities,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1687, \"to\": 1867, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The French Government spent around \\u20ac9 billion on this year's Olympic Games.\", \"from\": 1869, \"to\": 1944, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1873, \"end\": 1890, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_France\", \"score\": 0.9997247780573257, \"rank\": 0.00020830295427680734, \"text\": \"French Government\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Government_of_France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You can listen back here:    Main image: Supporters cheer on Jack Woolley of Team Ireland.\", \"from\": 1946, \"to\": 2036, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2007, \"end\": 2011, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jack_Harkness\", \"score\": 0.7488021545200296, \"rank\": 0.24162419076475752